    "testimonials_YEVBHF": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_8gw9eL": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Kenevo",
            "title": "Fabulous ergonomic gaming chair",
            "content": "<p>This chair not only looks very nice, it is also very versatile to adjust.<br/>On other chairs, I couldn't play for longer than 2 hours without getting neck and back pain. With the Autofull G7, I can sit on it all day and feel absolutely nothing, no pain or anything.<br/></p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_AdTWCV": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Ovidiu44",
            "title": "Very satisfied!",
            "content": "<p>Everything is as expected, quality materials, a premium and very comfortable gaming chair<br/>Worth the investment 100%<br/>The support service is prompt and very helpful.</p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_AYTJCb": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Spotjuh",
            "title": "Autofull M6 Ultra",
            "content": "<p>I didn't know what to expect from this chair at all but I'm so glad i have bought it. I was afraid that the seat cushion would be to firm but you really sit like a King on a throne.I really liked the manual aswell i understood everything. </p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_KwQpec": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Pedro S",
            "title": "5 stars, for now.",
            "content": "<p>So as of right now im giving it a 5 star review due to the resolution of an issue i had with the purchase of a c3 pro chair in black. When i bought it on the website it stated it had stock but a few days later after contacting support for not getting the tracking nr they told me they would only have stock of that chair in mid September. </p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_fUx6BP": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Johan",
            "title": "Satisfied",
            "content": "<p>Great updates on shipping, easy and fast delivery. There is one thing I would like to point out that was not easy about the delivery. Swedish PostNord don't help more than leaving the package out on the curb. I would have expected them to at least get them inside the building, maybe even to the elevator, but no. </p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_NQNwRP": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Johan",
            "title": "Extremely happy",
            "content": "<p>This is a first impression of mine and my wife's C3's which arrived yesterday evening. We have assembled the chairs and done some initial gaming and feeling how and if they work for us since after all they are our new work-space in competitive gaming which I've been part of for a very long time while my wife only started her career in gaming ~12 years ago.</p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_WQDXbB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Jason R., Austin, TX",
            "title": "Comfort, Support, and Features You Didn’t Know You Needed",
            "content": "<p>I’ve been using the M6 for about a month now, and honestly, it ticks almost every box. The lumbar support is next level — it actually moves with me when I shift positions, which is something I didn’t even know I needed until now. <br/></p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_jKGVRd": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Tony",
            "title": "Very nice chair",
            "content": "<p>The chair is very confy, and you can feel the quality of the chair.<br/>The funcions that the chair has are absolutly incredible and i finally found a chair that is good for my back.</p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_UTf7ti": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 5,
            "author": "Lukas",
            "title": "Auto Full M6 Ultra",
            "content": "<p>Also ich muss sagen das ist der beste Gamingstuhl auf den ich mich je hingesetzt habe, die Features sind alle Traumhaft also für den Preis finde ich das in Ordnung ich werde ab sofort nur noch mir Autofull Produkte kaufen Vielen dank Liebe AutoFull Community für die Top Qualität.</p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        },
        "testimonial_y88tnB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "round_avatar": true,
            "show_rating": true,
            "rating": 4,
            "author": "Tuukka",
            "title": "Arrived incredibly quickly!",
            "content": "<p>Arrived incredibly quickly!, and assembly was really easy too with great video tutorial! I've used the chair right away and I've been liked it! 5 stars!</p>",
            "more_url": ""
          }
        }
      },
